{"type":null,"faqId":41558,"title":"P8_为什么微信运动不会计步，或者计步数一直不增长？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">有两个问题会导致该问题</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">微信配置白名单延迟，导致手机型号未进入微信运动的白名单，此时需要重新退出微信然后登陆<span>.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">微信应用存在读取计步数有问题，导致计步数一直为<span>0</span>或者计步到某个数值以后一直不增长。此时有如下两种处理办法：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">(1).</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">查看微信是否有新版本，更新到新版本解决该问题<span>,</span>然后退出微信重新登录。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">(2).</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">先取消关注微信运动公众号，然后重新关注微信运动公众号即可。取消关注微信运动公号方法如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\"><img width=\"137\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092307611001.gif\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe4_d6xlc.png\">&nbsp;<span -converted-space=\"\">&nbsp;</span><img width=\"132\" height=\"258\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092308292002.gif\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe5_jgoo9.png\"><span -converted-space=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><img width=\"168\" height=\"262\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092308294003.jpg\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe6_aixeg.png\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">如果用户还需要了解微信运动的其他<span>FAQ</span>，建议用户在微信运动公众号中输入帮助，然后发送，微信运动会有<span>FAQ</span>推送：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto;\ntext-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black\"><img width=\"155\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092308283004.gif\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe7_yj8ya.png\"></span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":5,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7018","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442193302000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":343,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList"